SUMMARY:Sonoma Sips at Sonoma Valley Wineries
DESCRIPTION:Sampling premium Sonoma Valley wines doesn’t have to be expensive or intimidating. Sonoma Sips is a special partnership between the Sonoma Valley Visitors Bureau and Sonoma Valley Vintners &amp; Growers\, offering $15 tastings at more than 40 participating wineries throughout the valley.    From February 15 through March 15\, this introductory tasting price makes it easier than ever to explore the region’s world-class wines and picturesque vineyards. Sonoma Sips invites both first-time tasters and seasoned wine lovers to try something new or finally visit a winery that’s been on their list. Simply choose a participating winery or tasting room\, let the host know you’re there for Sonoma Sips\, and enjoy a curated tasting experience. A full list of participating wineries is available online.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/sonoma-sips-at-sonoma-valley-wineries/
LOCATION:Healdsburg, CA, 95448, United States
GEO:-122.8691609;38.6104658
CATEGORIES:Sonoma County,Tastings,Wine,Wine Tasting
