SUMMARY:Sip &amp; Paint at B.R. Cohn Winery
DESCRIPTION:Unleash your creativity with a guided painting experience overlooking their scenic vineyards\, perfectly paired with B.R. Cohn wines. This relaxed\, instructor-led session includes all painting materials and your first glass of wine to spark inspiration. Sip\, swirl\, and create as you take in the beautiful surroundings. Additional wines will be available for purchase\, making it easy to settle in and enjoy a memorable afternoon of art and wine.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/sip-paint-at-b-r-cohn-winery/
LOCATION:15000 Sonoma Highway, Glen Ellen, CA, 95442, United States
