SUMMARY:St Patrick’s Day Bar Crawl at Beer Baron Bar &amp; Kitchen
DESCRIPTION:The St. Patrick’s Day Bar Crawl in Santa Rosa invites guests to celebrate with green drinks\, festive energy\, and exclusive specials at some of the city’s best bars. Participants will hop between venues\, enjoying lively crowds\, themed cocktails\, and plenty of Irish-inspired cheer.    Tickets include 2–3 drinks or shots\, no cover at participating bars\, access to the mid-party and after party\, and exclusive drink and food specials at select locations. Guests also receive green and gold beads\, a Crawl With US stadium cup and bottle opener lanyard\, a custom event badge with vouchers\, and access to the official Santa Rosa pub crawl map. Professional photographers will capture the fun throughout the day.    Wear your green and get ready for a spirited celebration.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/st-patricks-day-bar-crawl-at-beer-baron-bar-kitchen/
LOCATION:614 4th St, , Santa Rosa,, CA, 95404,, United States
CATEGORIES:Celebration,Drink,Food,Holiday,Music,Sonoma County
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://winecountry-media.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2026/03/03201043/image.png
