SUMMARY:She’s All That’ Dinner at The Lodge at Dawn Ranch
DESCRIPTION:She’s All That Dinner at The Lodge at Dawn Ranch brings together three of Sonoma County’s inspiring female culinary leaders for a special collaboration celebrating International Women’s Month. The evening features Melissa McGaughey of Quail &amp; Condor\, Juliana Thorpe\, and Sarah Citron of Bricoleur Vineyards.    Set among Guerneville’s towering redwoods\, the intimate dinner features a multi-course tasting menu blending Chef Melissa’s Turkish-inspired pastry expertise with Chef Juliana’s South American–influenced California cuisine. Each course is paired with wines from Bricoleur Vineyards\, personally poured by Sarah Citron. A portion of proceeds benefits the V Foundation for Cancer Research\, supporting breast cancer research.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/shes-all-that-dinner-at-the-lodge-at-dawn-ranch/
LOCATION:16467 CA-116, Guerneville, CA, 95446, United States
CATEGORIES:Benefit,Celebration,Dining,Drink,Food,Food & Wine,Food and Wine Pairing,Sonoma County,Wine
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://winecountry-media.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2026/03/09233028/Screenshot-2026-03-09-at-8.22.40%E2%80%AFAM.png
