SUMMARY:St. Paddy’s Day at WonderStump
DESCRIPTION:St. Paddy’s Day with Pardon The Interruption at WonderStump invites guests to dance\, celebrate\, and wear their best green.    Pardon The Interruption brings a high-energy mix of ska-fueled funk\, rock\, reggae\, and soul\, turning the night into a full-body celebration with nonstop grooves and upbeat vibes. Surprise special guests will kick off the evening before the main performance.    This all-ages event offers non-alcoholic beverages and snacks available for purchase\, making it a fun and festive way to celebrate St. Patrick’s Day with friends and family.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/st-paddys-day-at-wonderstump/
LOCATION:301 Petaluma Boulevard North  Petaluma, CA 94952, Petaluma, CA, 94952, United States
CATEGORIES:Celebration,Dancing,Holiday,Live Music,Music,Performing Arts,Sonoma County
